headline: Thermo Fisher Scientific Enables Semiconductor Manufacturers to See the Unseen with Helios MX1 PFIB-SEM
summary: WALTHAM, Mass., October 28, 2025--From smartphones to autonomous cars to AI supercomputers, nearly every electronic innovation we use today depends on complicated structures at the atomic scale within silicon chips. As these chips increase in processing power and decrease in size, even the smallest fault can cause massive delays.
